import java.util.ArrayList;
    import java.util.List;

    public class Main {

        public static List<Integer> intersperse(List<Integer> numbers, int delimeter) {

            if (numbers.isEmpty()) {
                return new ArrayList<>();
            }

            List<Integer> result = new ArrayList<>();

            for (int i = 0; i < numbers.size() - 1; i++) {
                result.add(numbers.get(i));
                result.add(delimeter);
            }

            result.add(numbers.get(numbers.size() - 1));

            return result;
        }

        public static void main(String[] args) {
            List<Integer> numbers = new ArrayList<>();
            numbers.add(1);
            numbers.add(2);
            numbers.add(3);
            numbers.add(4);
            numbers.add(5);

            List<Integer> result = intersperse(numbers, 0);

            for (int num : result) {
                System.out.print(num + " ");
            }
        }
    }

import java.util.List;
    import java.util.Collections;

    public static List<Double> rescaleToUnit(List<Double> numbers) {

        double minNumber = Collections.min(numbers);
        double maxNumber = Collections.max(numbers);

        for (int i = 0; i < numbers.size(); i++) {
            numbers.set(i, (numbers.get(i) - minNumber) / (maxNumber - minNumber));
        }

        return numbers;
    }
